{"title":"乡音〔外一首〕","authors":["赵玉亮"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":10,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡音〔外一首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵玉亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山路旁依然能拾起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿时的几行脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小溪边依然能抓住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年的几串笑声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是婶娘那张豁牙的嘴里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然漏着我的乳名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么顺耳动听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只轻轻一声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就打湿了我的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以泥土浑然的气息漫过来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以大山宽厚的臂膀围过来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我奋力扑进这温馨的怀抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让大地的血脉充盈全身……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踮起脚尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我舒开一枝一叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍像田野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一株朴实的庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇曳着美丽的青春"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}